snippet.title: The Bride! | Official Teaser
snippet.description:
There’s a monster inside us all. #TheBrideMovie only in theaters March 6.

From Maggie Gyllenhaal (Academy Award-nominated writer/director of The Lost Daughter) and starring Academy Award nominee Jessie Buckley and Academy Award winner Christian Bale comes THE BRIDE! A bold, iconoclastic take on one of the world’s most compelling stories.

A lonely Frankenstein (Bale) travels to 1930s Chicago to ask groundbreaking scientist Dr. Euphronious (five-time Oscar nominee Annette Bening) to create a companion for him. The two revive a murdered young woman and The Bride (Buckley) is born. What ensues is beyond what either of them imagined: Murder! Possession! A wild and radical cultural movement! And outlaw lovers in a wild and combustible romance!

The film stars Buckley, Bale, Peter Sarsgaard, with Bening, Academy Award nominee Jake Gyllenhaal, and Oscar winner Penélope Cruz. Maggie Gyllenhaal directs from her own screenplay and produces alongside Oscar nominee Emma Tillinger Koskoff, Talia Kleinhendler and Osnat Handelsman Keren. The executive producers are Carla Raij, David Webb and Courtney Kivowitz. 

Gyllenhaal is supported behind the camera by a team of award-winning film artisans, including director of photography Lawrence Sher, production designer Karen Murphy, editor Dylan Tichenor, music supervisor Randall Poster, composer Hildur Gudnadóttir and costume designer Sandy Powell. 

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents A First Love Films / In The Current Company Production, A Maggie Gyllenhaal Film: THE BRIDE!. The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, only in theaters and IMAX in North America on March 6, 2026, and internationally beginning 4 March 2026.

【STORY】
悪魔の心臓を持つ「チェンソーマン」となり、公安対魔特異４課に所属するデビルハンターの少年・デンジ（戸谷菊之介）。
憧れのマキマ（楠木ともり）とのデートで浮かれている中、急な雨に見舞われ、
雨宿りしていると偶然“レゼ”（上田麗奈）という少女と出会った。
近所のカフェで働いているという彼女はデンジに優しく微笑み、二人は急速に親密に。
この出会いを境に、デンジの日常は変わり始めていく……

https://youtu.be/qYcU41ew_BM


━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
 “Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc” 
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
For the first time, Chainsaw Man slashes his way onto the big screen in an epic, action-fueled adventure that continues the hugely popular anime series. Denji worked as a Devil Hunter for the yakuza, trying to pay off the debt he inherited from his parents, until the yakuza betrayed him and had him killed. As he was losing consciousness, Denji’s beloved chainsaw-powered devil-dog, Pochita, made a deal with Denji and saved his life. This fused the two together, creating the unstoppable Chainsaw Man. Now, in a brutal war between devils, hunters, and secret enemies, a mysterious girl named Reze has stepped into his world, and Denji faces his deadliest battle yet, fueled by love in a world where survival knows no rules.

🦸‍♂  Avengers: Doomsday

Among Marvel fans, one of the most persistent rumors is the existence of Avengers: Doomsday. The title alone has sparked waves of speculation, suggesting a darker and more catastrophic chapter in the MCU. Many believe the film could introduce Doctor Doom as the ultimate antagonist, uniting Earth’s heroes in their most desperate battle yet. With the Avengers’ roster constantly evolving, theories about who will lead the team into this fight dominate fan discussions.

The speculative storyline points to multiverse incursions colliding into a singular devastating event, forcing the Avengers to confront impossible odds. This idea aligns with ongoing Marvel arcs, where dimensions crumble and alliances are tested. Fans envision massive set pieces spanning multiple universes, with characters from past phases reuniting alongside newcomers in a final stand against overwhelming destruction. Doomsday could become the MCU’s most expansive and emotionally charged narrative to date.

Audiences have also been buzzing about casting possibilities, with rumors ranging from returning veterans to surprising additions. Online communities are already filled with imagined trailers and posters showcasing potential matchups between beloved heroes and Doom himself. If Avengers: Doomsday becomes reality, it could redefine Marvel’s cinematic landscape and mark the beginning of a bold new era for the franchise.

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: Dead by Daylight: Sinister Grace – The Krasue Joins the Fog | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
When darkness fell, The Krasue awakened… 

Inspired by Thai folklore, play as The Krasue, a gruesome Killer with two terrifying forms, and Vee Boonyasak, an electrifying survivor from the rising punk band Axekick. Step into a terrifying world rooted in visceral body-horror. Dead by Daylight: Sinister Grace, Now Available! 

*Coming September 25th for Switch.  

Learn More:  http://dbd.game/4nhUkzK

Trapped forever in a realm of eldritch evil where even death is not an escape, four determined Survivors face a bloodthirsty Killer in a vicious game of nerve and wits. Pick a side and step into a world of tension and terror with horror gaming's best asymmetrical multiplayer.
